OOC: Megatron is back at the Predacon Cave.

    Megatron glares at Terrorsaur, "Where was I? You imputent little winged 
lizard! As if you are the commander and I am your minion! Cross that boundry 
agian and you will be a red scrap pile, got it?!?!"
    He then turns to the others. "Well done on the defence while I was away. 
I should inform you all that we will be moving up in the world. Moving right 
up into the Armada."
